  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main purpose of this project is to strengthen the internal and external logistics capacities for implementing  Disaster Risk reduction programme. The programme works with various disaster risk reduction actors (Local authorities, communities, Oxfam staff and Oxfam partner staff) in mitigating, preparing and responding to disaster situation by enabling at risk communities/population in the Northern Department, Port au Prine , South East and Nippes to respond rapidly and efficiently to a disaster situation</narrative>
